{
  "stem": "18813.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 97.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] every night she was crying, crying, and crying.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said, what do you want?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You want to go back?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I take you back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You want something-- to buy you something?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I buy you something.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I didn't know what she wanted.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she said she wants a Jesus.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She was-- I went out, and I bought a picture of Jesus.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I hanged that on my bed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And every night, the little girl was kneeling down and saying her prayers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And as soon as she finished prayers, she stopped crying.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that's my story about the liberation with my little girl, who is-- lives now in Lugano, Switzerland, very religious, very religious.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My grandson visited her.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I told him, don't go Friday night, please, because they won't open the door-- the Shabbos, OK?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he went after, waited [LAUGHS] on Saturday when we finished to go.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But thank God she's alive.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I love her, and she loves me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Did you have an opportunity to go back to your father's business?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I went-- as a matter of fact, I told you the story that we hide some merchandise.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And after the war, I took the police with me because there was a hairdresser there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the business was three times the-- big than the apartment here, was three, four chairs.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they got for free.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So-- and I went to have my hair done with my girlfriend who lives in Montreal.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I said, [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Hanka, ?] I have to have my hair done.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I recognized that nothing was touched there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I took the police.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I took out some merchandise with my friends.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
